# Day 12 – Kubernetes Deployment

## Purpose
EN: Deploy applications into Kubernetes clusters.  
CZ: Nasazovat aplikace do Kubernetes clusterů.

## Prompt
EN:
```
Create Deployment, Service, Ingress, ConfigMap, resource limits,
and liveness/readiness probes for a demo app.
```

CZ:
```
Vytvoř Deployment, Service, Ingress, ConfigMap, resource limity
a liveness/readiness probe pro demo aplikaci.
```
